title: Episode 111: Feat. Joseline Hernandez
itunes:title: Episode 111: Feat. Joseline Hernandez
description:
Joseline Hernandez sits with the ladies of Lip Service to discuss a wide range of topics including how motherhood has impacted her life. Joseline explains why she believes dating both a man and a woman at the same time would be ideal for her. She even opens up about who has been her best sexual experiences, both male and female. Joseline also details how to help Puerto Rico through her non profit organization.
